Language choice
List of the MIDP Java phones ordered by performance (better on top). To add your cell phone to this list download TastePhone directly on your mobile phone from :
http://wap.club-java.com/en

You can also read a longer list of MIDP Java phones, which have only downloaded TastePhone without sending results.
